            </div>
            <div class="breadcrumb">
                <a href="catalog.html">培训目录</a>
                <span>></span>
                <span>网络软件生态</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="slide-title">
            <div class="module-icon">🧩</div>
            <h1 class="main-title">统一的软件定义基础设施</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">全面、开放、可编程的 NVIDIA 网络软件生态系统</p>
        </div>

        <main class="content-main">
            <div class="pillar-card">
                <div class="pillar-header">
                    <div class="pillar-icon">🛠️</div>
                    <h3 class="pillar-title">基础软件与驱动</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="pillar-description">为 NVIDIA 网络硬件提供稳定、高性能的底层支持，是发挥硬件全部潜能的基石。</p>
                <ul class="tech-list">
                    <li><strong>MLNX_OFED:</strong> 适配器核心驱动程序包</li>
                    <li><strong>Adapter Firmware:</strong> 适配器固件与更新工具</li>
                    <li><strong>Switch Firmware:</strong> 交换机固件与管理</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="pillar-card">
                <div class="pillar-header">
                    <div class="pillar-icon">🌐</div>
                    <h3 class="pillar-title">网络操作系统与管理</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="pillar-description">提供开放、灵活的网络操作系统和强大的集中管理平台，简化数据中心网络运维。</p>
                <ul class="tech-list">
                    <li><strong>NVIDIA Cumulus Linux:</strong> 开放式网络操作系统</li>
                    <li><strong>NVIDIA Air:</strong> 模拟 Cumulus 环境的平台</li>
                    <li><strong>NetQ:</strong> 全生命周期网络验证与排错</li>
                    <li><strong>UFM Platform:</strong> InfiniBand 集群管理平台</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="pillar-card">
                <div class="pillar-header">
                    <div class="pillar-icon">🚀</div>
                    <h3 class="pillar-title">加速与卸载平台</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="pillar-description">通过 DPU 硬件和 DOCA 软件开发套件，将网络、存储和安全任务从 CPU 卸载，释放算力，加速应用。</p>
                <ul class="tech-list">
                    <li><strong>NVIDIA DOCA:</strong> DPU 软件开发框架</li>
                    <li><strong>BlueField DPU:</strong> 数据中心基础设施处理器</li>
                    <li><strong>DPU & SuperNIC:</strong> 加速云原生超级计算</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer class="slide-footer">
            <div class="presenter-info">
                <div class="presenter-name">Vincent</div>
                <div class="presenter-title">技术总监</div>
            </div>
            <div class="slide-number">4 / 9</div>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <div class="navigation-controls">
        <button class="nav-button" onclick="goBack()">← 上一模块</button>
        <button class="nav-button" onclick="nextModule()">下一模块 →</button>
        <div class="nav-hint">使用左右箭头键导航</div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function goBack() {
            window.location.href = 'nvlink.html';
        }

        function nextModule() {
            alert('下一模块：网络适配器');
            // 后续可以跳转到 adapters.html
        }

        document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
            if (e.code === 'ArrowLeft') {
                e.preventDefault();
                goBack();
            } else if (e.code === 'ArrowRight' || e.code === 'Space') {
                e.preventDefault();
                nextModule();
            } else if (e.code === 'Escape') {
                window.location.href = 'catalog.html';
            }
        });

        document.querySelector('.breadcrumb a').addEventListener('click', function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            window.location.href = 'catalog.html';
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
